quran[8{c,v,t}:
12,15,"iss terhan israar kar ke jab woh ussay le gay aur unhon ne tey kar liya ke usay aik andhay kunvey mein chore den, to hum ne yousuf ko wahi ki ke"" aik waqt aeye ga jab to un logon ko un ki yeh harkat jitye ga, yeh apne feal ke nataij se be khabar hain """
12,16,shaam ko woh rotay pitte apne baap ke paas aeye
12,17,"aur kaha"" abba jaan, hum daud ka muqaabla karne mein lag gay thay aur yousuf ko hum ne apne samaan ke paas chore diya tha ke itnay mein bheria aa kar ussay kha gaya aap hamari baat ka yaqeen nah karen ge chahay hum sachey hi hon """
12,18,"aur woh yousuf ke kameez par jhoot moot ka khoon laga kar aeye thay yeh sun kar un ke baap ne kaha"" balkay tumahray nafs ne tumahray liye aik barray kaam ko aasaan bana diya acha, sabr karoon ga aur bakhoobi karoon ga, jo baat tum bana rahay ho is par Allah hi se madad mangi ja sakti hai """
12,19,"idhar aik qaafla aaya aur uss ne apne saqqay (water carrier) ko pani laane ke liye bheja saqqay (water carrier) ne jo kunvey (well) mein doll dala to ( yousuf ko dekh kar ) pukaar utha"" mubarak ho, yahan to aik larka hai"" un logon ne is ko maal tijarat samajh kar chhupa liya, halaank jo kuch woh kar rahay thay khuda is se bakhabar tha"
12,20,aakhir-kaar unhon ne is ko thori si qeemat par chanddarhamonke iwaz beech dala aur woh is ki qeemat ke maamla mein kuch ziyada ke umeed waar nah thay
12,21,"misar ke jis shakhs ne usay khareeda is ne apni biwi se kaha"" iss ko achi terhan rakhna, baeed nahi ke yeh hamaray liye mufeed saabit ho ya hum usay beta bana len"" is terhan hum ne yousuf ke liye uss sarzamen mein qadam jamanay ki soorat nikaali aur usay maamla fehmi ki taleem dainay ka intizam kya Allah apna kaam kar ke rehta hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
12,22,"aur jab woh apni poori jawani ko pouncha to hum ne usay qowat faisla aur ilm ataa kya, iss terhan hum naik logon ko jaza dete hain"
